        <h3>Dream Catcher</h3>
        <p>Dream Catcher is an app that allows you to log your dreams and motivations so that you can keep a track of all your lucid memories.
          <br><br>
          To find symbolism and resemblance and bring people together we've added the functionality of visibility on the posts.Not only can you log your dreams the users also have the ability to share their dreams or keep it private in their profile.
          <br><br>
          The journal posts that are public are open to other viewers to comment on. You can also edit your journal posts or delete it.
          <br><br>
        </p>
